gh Environment: </strong>The story unravels through the setting itself - explore and interact with your surroundings to uncover the haunting tale that lies within.<br></li><li><strong>Intense Horror Experience: </strong>Simulating the terror of a home invasion, this game is a test of nerves - hide, strategize, and when necessary, confront your unseen enemy.<br></li><li><strong>Survival Strategy: </strong>You are prey in this game, and survival means thinking fast. Your choices are limited and critical, so every move counts.<br></li><li><strong>]Global Accessibility: </strong>Supporting multiple languages including English, German, Portuguese, Spanish, French, Chinese, Japanese, and Russian, to welcome players from across the globe.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"I Can See You\" is more than a game; it's an exercise in survival, a challenge to your senses and your wit. Do you have what it takes to survive?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar